{"tid":1779542,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"白日既匿，繼以朗月，同乘並載，以游後園","createTime":"2019-12-11T17:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T10:09:13.000Z","uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2430526fd8b36a0d627204677687ae6a9b403bda","tid":1779542,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T17:46:11.000Z","msg":"「白日既匿，繼以朗月，同乘並載，以游後園，輿輪徐動，賓從無聲，今果分別，各在一方。」<br />\n<br />\n召喚魏晉同好，其實諗返而家同嗰時都有啲似，政治昏暗，有志者無事可做，只能風花雪月，卻道天涼好個秋。"},{"pid":"55d798f0ae369cabd3fb1717025bb8a8950f61ec","tid":1779542,"uid":294221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ow4Z2BY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fow4Z2BY.jpg&h=1345ec69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人最強後盾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/addoiluk1023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faddoiluk1023&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnADC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=23636a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/addoiluk1023</a>"},{"pid":"a86de5d7a43f0801f428d8bbdf5fb3a910f823f9","tid":1779542,"uid":73406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T22:43:47.000Z","msg":"呢篇係魏文帝嘅與朝歌令吳質書嚟喎...更多嘅係遊南皮回憶。另一篇講明佢傷感嘅原因係徐陳應劉一時俱逝。<br />\n<br />\n魏晉南北朝寫呢啲嘅能手都係交返俾左思鮑照"},{"pid":"b212d5633c1877d1e9cfa3009aa5c43a25f76d1b","tid":1779542,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a86de5d7a43f0801f428d8bbdf5fb3a910f823f9","tid":1779542,"uid":73406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T22:43:47.000Z","msg":"呢篇係魏文帝嘅與朝歌令吳質書嚟喎...更多嘅係遊南皮回憶。另一篇講明佢傷感嘅原因係徐陳應劉一時俱逝。<br />\n<br />\n魏晉南北朝寫呢啲嘅能手都係交返俾左思鮑照"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"想講嘅係嗰個年代上至帝王，下至門人食客，都有種世局動盪，今日唔知聽日事嘅心態，呢個又病死，嗰個又戰死，歡樂嘅日子就只能回味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b